<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Password Reset - Light Tackle</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #653AAD, orangered);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .body-content {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .body-content p {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .reset-token {
      background: #f5f5f5;
      border: 2px dashed #653AAD;
      color: #333;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-family: monospace;
    }

    .reset-token p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .reset-token p b {
      color: orangered;
    }

    .footer {
      background: #f4f4f4;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }

    a {
      color: orangered;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      Light Tackle Password Reset
    </header>
    
    <div class="body-content">
      <p>Dear <%= user.name %>,</p>
      
      <p>We received a request to reset your password for Light Tackle. Please use the following token to reset your password:</p>

      <div class="reset-token">
        <p><b>Token:</b> <%= user.token %></p>
        <p><b>Expires In:</b> 10 minutes</p>
      </div>

      <p>If you did not request this reset, please ignore this email or <a href="mailto:support@lighttackle">contact our support team</a>.</p>

      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p><b>Light Tackle Team</b></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>You are receiving this email because you requested a password reset on Light Tackle.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
